name: Login, list post, create, publish and list post

elements.name: Ingresar con cuenta válida, Listar Post, Crear Post, Publicar Post, Listar Posts

steps.name: I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-editor-title"
I enter "<TITLE_POST>" into input field having css selector "textarea"
I enter "<DESCRIPTION_POST>" into input field having css selector "p"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-publishmenu-trigger"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-publishmenu-button"
